ContentClassification.TableDescription: 1990-95 Basic Table – Male. Basis: Age Last Birthday. Minimum Select Age: 0 Maximum Select Age: 99. Minimum Ultimate Age: 25. Maximum Ultimate Age: 124.
ContentClassification.Comments: Study Data: Derived from age nearest birthday 1990-95 Basic Tables (See SOA Table Identities 369 and 371). Methodology: Ultimate developed from an average of q(x) and q(x+1). Select developed from formula: q'([x]+t-1)=(C)q([x]+t-1) + (1-C)q([x+1]+t-1) where C=.5 for age 0-98 and then a special formula for age 99 NOTE: a prior version of this table contained “draft” rates. The table has been updated to reflect the final set of published rates. Data Transcription Errors: None. Data Certified: 06/2013
